,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"這以外的話，知道聯絡方式的還有日菜學姊跟，\n跟……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev58-ep5-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"算、算了，幾個人什麼的根本不重要吧。\n就算知道了很多不聯絡也沒意義！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev58-ep5-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"……難得都交換了，就連絡看看吧。\n像是昨天的道謝，也沒有好好地說","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev58-ep5-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"好。\n『昨天辛苦了』……這怎麼好像，有點生硬","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev58-ep5-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"不行，重來。唔～嗯……\n『昨天辛苦啦。糖果很好吃。就這樣』……\n還是很生硬嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev58-ep5-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"『昨天辛苦啦。糖果店也還不差喔』……\n不對，還不差，這個說法有點失禮。\n要用其他說法才行","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev58-ep5-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"『是很棒的店』『很可愛』\n『很開心』『很感動』……總覺得，哪個都不對","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev58-ep5-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"唉。不行了。完全想不到好的話。\n我跟Afterglow的大家傳訊息是怎麼做的去了？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev58-ep5-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"大多都是看了之後沒回覆啊。\n或是只回覆一句話啊，給大家的話……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev58-ep5-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"目前為止這樣就可以了，但這次可不能再這樣。\n不過，一開始的訊息太生硬的話\n搞不好又要被有咲說是硬派風格","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev58-ep5-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"……啊〜〜，不行啦！　算了，今天就先不傳了吧。\n……嗯？\n啊……是有咲傳訊來……！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev58-ep5-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"我看看……\n『昨天辛苦了。\n糖果很好吃耶。再約喔！』咦……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"ev58-ep5-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"蘭","body":"啊哈哈哈。跟我想的文字幾乎一樣嘛。\n太生硬了啦","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeF